{
  "texts": [
    "Interpretability ensures that the chatbot's behavior can be traced back to specific rules, algorithms, or data sources 46.",
    "Empathy is the ability to understand and share the feelings of another person.",
    "Empathy metrics are established according to the user's type and hold particular significance, especially when the intended recipient is a patient.",
    "These metrics ensure that the chatbots consider end-users emotional support, trust, concerns, fairness, and health literacy [47] [48] [49] [50].",
    "Empathy also plays a crucial role in building trust between users and chatbots."
  ]
}